data.description: Charming country house close to the lake, less than a mile to the boat ramp, makes a perfect blend of lake and country life! Home has been freshly painted and is ready for immediate occupancy. 1 Bedroom, 1 full bath with single vanity and tub/shower combo. Full kitchen with gas cooking, ample counter space, and a laundry area. A bonus room off the bedroom could be used as additional sleeping space and screened in porch. Metal roof, Double pane windows and new Metal siding. The 1.37 acres is fully fenced with a wood privacy fence along the front, separate high fenced garden, a barn, a chicken coop, a carport, and an additional storage building. Landscaping is full of flowering trees, plants, and bushes. Very nice, well maintained home. Call us to see your new vacation cabin or nightly rental today.
